	<p>When WebCOBRA was launched we included a highly sophisticated API that was unique across Travis' product line. Instead of asking our support staff to learn how to program, we setup a center for IT staff and developers to submit questions, download sample code, and help the community out. An example of this working perfectly is highlighted on: <a href="http://devcenter.webcobra.com/conversations/156.aspx">http://devcenter.webcobra.com/conversations/156.aspx</a></p>
